OL,3,CCeramics firm to halt production for
OL,4,C90 days amid falling demand
OL,6,FStaffordshire-based ceramics firm
OL,7,FWedgwood will temporarily pause
OL,8,Fproduction for up to 90 days, with 70
OL,9,Femployees placed on temporary leave.
OL,11,FFiskars Group, which owns Wedgwood,
OL,12,Fsaid it has too much of its products
OL,13,Fin its inventory because of lower
OL,14,Fconsumer demand.
OL,16,FTours of the factory in Barlaston,
OL,17,Fpart of the popular World of Wedgwood
OL,18,Ftourist destination, will also be
OL,19,Fsuspended during the period.
