OL,3,CCeramics firm to halt production for
OL,4,C90 days amid falling demand
OL,6,FFiskars Group Senior Vice President
OL,7,FSjoerd Leeflang said: "There is a
OL,8,Fglobal instability in terms of what
OL,9,Fthe demand is for our products made in
OL,10,FEngland versus what we have already in
OL,11,Fthe inventory.
OL,13,F"If we were to continue production we
OL,14,Fwould be producing too much stock for
OL,15,Fthe various markets where we sell.
OL,17,F"Our employees are extremely important
OL,18,F- we will take care of them, we will
OL,19,Fpay their full salary for the rest of
OL,20,Fthe period and we will welcome them
OL,21,Fback at the beginning of January.
