OL,3,CCeramics firm to halt production for
OL,4,C90 days amid falling demand
OL,6,F"You don't know what is happening in
OL,7,Fthe world economy, I can't say for
OL,8,Fsure the economy will change, but
OL,9,FWedgwood has a commitment to be made
OL,10,Fin England.
OL,12,F"We look after our colleagues in the
OL,13,Ffactory so we really keep our craft
OL,14,Falive because that is important for
OL,15,Fthe future of this brand.
OL,17,F"Trust Wedgwood, trust the owner of
OL,18,FWedgwood, Fiskars Group, we are here
OL,19,Ffor the long term, we do this to look
OL,20,Fafter a healthy future for the
OL,21,FWedgwood brand."
