OL,6,FThe factory produces high-end and
OL,7,Fbespoke products, including
OL,8,Fhandcrafted pieces in fine bone china
OL,9,Fand its signature Jasperware.
OL,11,FThe firm said its skilled artisans
OL,12,Fstill use techniques pioneered by
OL,13,Ffounding English pottery designer and
OL,14,Fmanufacturer Josiah Wedgwood, who was
OL,15,Fborn in Burslem, Staffordshire, in
OL,16,F1730.
